! rebin_fts

! PURPOSE

! Rebin and downsample an FTS data set by a factor

! SYNTAX

! @ rebin_fts input_file output_file factor

! tell CLASS to be quiet
sic MESSAGE CLASS S=FE

set angle sec

say Rebinning &1 to CLASS file &2 with factor &3

file in &1

find /telescope 30M-F0*

file out &2 single /overwrite

for i 1 to found

    get next

    ! SET REST FREQUENCY TO 12CO(2-1)
    modify frequency 230538.000

    ! SMOOTH FTS 195kHz DATA
    smooth box &3

    ! WRITE TO THE OUTPUT FILE
    write    

next
